00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:33.220
Cool.

00:31:33.220 --> 00:31:36.010
So I guess a lot of
you probably think

00:31:36.010 --> 00:31:39.220
that I'm here to present
the secrets around the Holy

00:31:39.220 --> 00:31:40.870
Grail of retention.

00:31:40.870 --> 00:31:42.940
If I happen to do
